OL,3,CConman took thousands from pensioners
OL,4,Cfor work he never intended to do
OL,6,FA man who exploited elderly people for
OL,7,Fmoney by taking thousands of pounds
OL,8,Ffor manual work on their houses has
OL,9,Fbeen described as "despicable".
OL,11,FCraig Francis appeared at Swansea
OL,12,FCrown Court after targeting three
OL,13,Felderly people in order to pay for
OL,14,F"alcohol and drugs".
OL,16,FHe knocked on the doors of his
OL,17,Fvictims, who were in their 70s and
OL,18,F80s, and persuaded them to pay him for
OL,19,Fodd-jobs and building work before
OL,20,Fsimply pocketing the cash, the court
OL,21,Fheard.
