OL,3,CConman took thousands from pensioners
OL,4,Cfor work he never intended to do
OL,6,FThe prosecutor, Caitlin Brazel,
OL,7,Frecounted how all three incidents
OL,8,Fhappened in the village of Skewen near
OL,9,FNeath during a period of a few weeks.
OL,10,FHe was finally detained when the son
OL,11,Fof one of his victims, along with the
OL,12,Faid of neighbours, restrained him
OL,13,Fafter he revisited the property in
OL,14,Fsearch of more money.
OL,16,FSending 36-year-old Francis to prison,
OL,17,Fa judge described his exploitation of
OL,18,Fhis elderly victims as "despicable".
