OL,3,CConman took thousands from pensioners
OL,4,Cfor work he never intended to do
OL,6,FThe court heard how Francis had
OL,7,Fapproached an 81-year-old woman
OL,8,Foffering to do any work needed.
OL,10,FMentioning that the rear guttering
OL,11,Fneeded fixing, they agreed upon a
OL,12,Fprice of #240. Francis proceeded to
OL,13,Fask the woman to drive him to a shop
OL,14,Fin order to buy supplies. He told the
OL,15,Fvictim the items would be delivered in
OL,16,Fa few days.
