OL,3,CConman took thousands from pensioners
OL,4,Cfor work he never intended to do
OL,6,FHe returned to her property the
OL,7,Ffollowing day, requesting a further
OL,8,F#148 for more items, as well as a lift
OL,9,Fto Neath. The woman refused the
OL,10,Frequest and the defendant left.
OL,12,FAlthough the victim had no further
OL,13,Fcontact with Francis, she claims she
OL,14,Fsaw him knocking at other doors along
OL,15,Fthe same street.
OL,17,FThe second victim, an 81-year-old man
OL,18,Fwith hearing loss, had paid Francis a
OL,19,Fsum of #2,700 for the promised jobs.
