OL,3,CConman took thousands from pensioners
OL,4,Cfor work he never intended to do
OL,6,FFrancis was arrested and answered "no
OL,7,Fcomment" to all questions asked in his
OL,8,Ffirst interview before making full
OL,9,Fadmissions in his second interview
OL,10,Fwhen he told officers he had spent the
OL,11,Fmoney on alcohol and drugs.
OL,13,FCraig Francis, of Lon Las Villas, Lon
OL,14,FLas, Skewen, had previously pleaded
OL,15,Fguilty to three counts of fraud by
OL,16,Ffalse representation when he appeared
OL,17,Fin the dock for sentencing.
OL,19,FHe had five previous convictions for
OL,20,Fsix offences including a robbery from
OL,21,F2009.
