OL,3,CConman took thousands from pensioners
OL,4,Cfor work he never intended to do
OL,6,FHe said Francis took the money from
OL,7,Fthe householders because he saw them
OL,8,Fas "easy marks" and he said he had no
OL,9,Fdoubt the defendant had taken the cash
OL,10,Fwith no intention of ever doing any
OL,11,Fwork.
OL,13,FWith a one-third discount for his
OL,14,Fguilty plea, Francis was sentenced to
OL,15,F24 weeks in prison. Francis will serve
OL,16,Fup to half the sentence in custody
OL,17,Fbefore being released on licence to
OL,18,Fserve the remainder in the community.
